Module kivakit.microservice
Package com.telenav.kivakit.microservice.protocols.rest.openapi

Annotation Type OpenApiIncludeMember

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({FIELD,METHOD}) public @interface OpenApiIncludeMember
Indicates that a member (method or field) should be included in the OpenAPI specification produced for a MicroserviceRestService
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
